Download Source From:
*********************
ftp://ftp.gnu.org/gnu/m4/
ftp://ftp.gnu.org/gnu/autoconf/
ftp://ftp.gnu.org/gnu/automake/
ftp://ftp.gnu.org/gnu/libtool/

*****************************
Build In The Following Order:
*****************************
m4
autoconf
automake
libtool

cd plfs/trunk
./autogen.sh
./configure
make all install
